<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>3</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;font-family:helvetica;">TrollKingdom has NO involvement in this board</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> (unless they paid off HF and are using him as a puppet admin <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :eek --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/eek.gif ALT=":eek"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   ). Decker's only posted here once, and Sardy won't even respond on the subject even though I've sent him two PMs about SSUG.  <br>
